{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"API Collection","title":"TokensProvider Implementations","role":"collectionGroup"},"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeskeletoncomponenttokensprovider\/tokensprovider-implementations"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider\/checkInstances(count:for:)"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider":{"title":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of skeleton"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"skeleton"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSkeleton"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SkeletonComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"skeleton"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Skeleton"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeskeletoncomponenttokensprovider","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider/checkInstances(count:for:)":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeskeletoncomponenttokensprovider\/checkinstances(count:for:)","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/O